title: Merkel: still many challenges ahead for Brexit
text:
Merkel: still many challenges ahead for Brexit 12:01pm EDT - 00:55 
German Chancellor Angela Merkel said she was pleased about the Brexit transition deal reached between the UK and the EU but says many problems remain. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
